                <mxCell id="elevator:state:Elevator:Idle" value="Idle&lt;br&gt;──────────────────&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;entry /&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;self.direction = Stopped;&lt;br&gt;self.next_stop_floor = 0;&lt;br&gt;select any req from instances of Request where request_id == self.r14_request_id;&lt;br&gt;if (req != empty) {&lt;br&gt;  generate Request_assigned(target_floor: req.destination_floor) to self;&lt;br&gt;} else {&lt;br&gt;  select any disp from instances of Dispatcher;&lt;br&gt;  generate Elevator_available(queue_length: 0) to disp;&lt;br&gt;}" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=10;fontFamily=Courier New;" parent="1" vertex="1">
